Introduction

Sullin is a Thai singer under MODHAUS.

On April 2, 2024, Sullin was introduced as the twenty-second member of the girl group tripleS under MODHAUS. She debuted with tripleS on May 8, 2024, with the album "ASSEMBLE24".

As a member of tripleS, Sullin was placed in the sub-unit Glow.
